@DATABASE "Yie-ar Kung Fu"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - Y - Yie-ar Kung Fu"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - Y
                   ====================================

                              Yie-ar Kung Fu
                              ==============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(29483,255)"}         29483,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Energy" rxs "address command zxampoke(61482,0)"}         61482,0
@{"Strength = x   " rxs "address command zxampoke(29974,255)"}         29974,x (x= 1-255) 
@{"One Hit Kills  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(61461,175)"}         61461,175


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         The "Strength = x" POKE will give equal
                         strength to BOTH players. Only really
                         useful if you like a longer fight.

                         The "One Hit Kills" means that you only
                         have to hit the opponent once to win.
                         Don't worry though, the reverse is not
                         true.


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
